      intro_title: "A word from the author",
      intro_text: "This site was created for everyone who does not always carry a printed pocket prayer book. Today — in the age of computers, smartphones and constant haste — a digital prayer book can hit the mark: after all, the phone, with all its pros and cons, is always at hand.\n\nFor us Christians, regular prayer should bind us together in our relationship with God. That is why, in a busy world, it is so important to reach for prayer and to care for that bond — at the bus stop, on a journey, during a break at work or in the evening before sleep.\n\nMay this humble companion help you remain with the Lord every day. Semper fidelis — ever faithful.",
